{"tid":2314067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都朗讀嗰陣都堅持講廣東話？","createTime":"2020-12-06T09:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T09:23:36.000Z","uid":142242,"like":68,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0168e5609095ff32397d9b93781b6f2674e9f1ea","tid":2314067,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:30:32.000Z","msg":"社會上大部分比較正式嘅文章都用所謂<span class=\"red\">「書面語」（實際上係北京官話白話文，被神化成「書面語」，粵語文就被貶為「口語」）</span>，有無人都朗讀呢啲所謂「書面語」都會堅持翻譯返做粵語？<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n我們 -》<span class=\"gold\">我哋</span><br />\n他/她 -》<span class=\"gold\">佢</span><br />\n我的電話 -》<span class=\"gold\">我部電話</span><br />\n我在看書 -》<span class=\"gold\">我睇緊書</span><br />\n很開心地上學 -》<span class=\"gold\">好開心咁返學</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就好似新聞既社評摘要咁，即使篇文係「書面語」，但個主播都會用通順嘅廣東話讀返出嚟，唔會逐字照讀（請原諒我share CCTVB新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1qtNlsp-OfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1qtNlsp-OfQ&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2kWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=c30b9623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1qtNlsp-OfQ</a><br />\n<br />\n受到固有中文教育影響，而家社會上主流仲係覺得所謂「書面語」比較正式，粵語文只係「口語」。咁既然做唔到「我手寫我口」，我起碼都想我講嘢同朗讀嗰陣可以講返真正嘅粵語，所以會翻譯返做通順嘅粵語，唔使俾北京官話控制住呀"},{"pid":"7118be3b14e3cb2cb976d682fb7eb73cb92d7342","tid":2314067,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:34:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e8f38504f9e8f75d28153a5e54fe0b403cf443ae","tid":2314067,"uid":249162,"like":6,"dislike":29,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"書面語就書面語，白話文係文言文既係之乎者也，同乜鳩北京話冇LA撚，北京支那畜係唔識字的，識既只係殘體字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da6d5ba96cc24d971a92bc3c9a8587d7c50315f","tid":2314067,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09